<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='365390' id='t-365390'>&quot;It's like living in a submarine.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='367040' id='t-367040'>This is crew compartment.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='368326' id='t-368326'>It switches, so what's
