<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='377255' id='t-377255'>This is a 20-man version
for going to Jupiter:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='379431' id='t-379431'>bunks, storm cellars, exercise room.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='381227' id='t-381227'>You know, it was going
to be a nice, long trip.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='383898' id='t-383898'>The Air Force version:
here we have a military version.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='388111' id='t-388111'>This is the kind of stuff
that's not been declassified,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='390725' id='t-390725'>just that people managed to sneak
