<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='422315' id='t-422315'>and then all those paths came to a halt.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:15
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='424290' id='t-424290'>Results: none.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='425775' id='t-425775'>This project is hereby terminated.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='427803' id='t-427803'>So that's the end.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:20
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='429705' id='t-429705'>All I can say in closing is:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='431330' id='t-431330'>we heard yesterday that one of the 10
