<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='443823' id='t-443823'>and everybody says,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='445442' id='t-445442'>&quot;Well, what are we going to do?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='447019' id='t-447019'>And Orion is really one
