<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='454091' id='t-454091'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:46
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='455966' id='t-455966'>So I'm going to tell you
